                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#2r"/>
                           <desc>Short medical prescription in Amharic.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="am"><gap reason="illegible"/> ፍሬ፡ ፯<surplus>፯</surplus>ቱን፡ ፯ቀን፡ ፯ወር፡ ሊይልቅ፡ ፯ቀን፡ ሲቀረው፡ ፯ቱን፡ ለ፩ቀን፡ እስከ፡ ፯ቀን፡ ድረስ፡ 
                              በትንሽ፡ ሳይበዛ፡ በነጭ፡ ማር፡ በጥዋት፡ ሽንት፡ ሻትሸን፡ ከሰው፡ ሳትነጋገር፡ በማር፡ ለውሶ፡ በትክል፡ ድንጋይ፡ ቆማ፡ 
                              ፊትዋን፡ ወደ፡ ምስራቅ፡ ምልሳ፡ ተዋጠው፡ </q>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#4r"/>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">A short ownership note mentioning <persName ref="PRS15433Zagiyorgis"/>, <persName ref="PRS15435IyasusMDM"/>,
                              <persName ref="PRS15434WaldaDawitWS"/>, and <persName ref="PRS15444MazmuraDeng"/>.
                           </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ 
                              ዘዘጊዮርጊስ፡ ወመምህሩ፡ ኢያሱስ፡ ሞአ፡ በእደ፡ ማርያም፡ ወአቡሁ፡ ወልደ፡ ዳዊት፡ ወመዝሙረ፡ ድንግል፡ ሲራክ፡</hi></q>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#78vb"/>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">A short ownership note mentioning <persName ref="PRS15433Zagiyorgis"/>, <persName ref="PRS15444MazmuraDeng"/>, and 
                              <persName ref="PRS15445GermaIya"/>.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ 
                              ዘዘጊዮርጊስ፡ ወዘአቡሁ፡ መዝሙረ፡ ድንግል፡ ሲራክ፡ <unclear>ወእኁሁ፡</unclear> ግርማ፡ ኢያሱስ፡</hi></q>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus from="79ra" to="79vc"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Different prayers, written by a crude
                              late-19th-century hand, with numerous corrections, making them
                              illegible. These prayers may be pen trials.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#80ra"/>
                           <desc>Short fragment of <title ref="LIT2361somade"/>, written probably by
                              the main hand.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#80va"/>
                           <desc>Short medical prescription in Amharic against malarian
                              fever.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="am">የሀሎ፡ ለዓለም፡ የጨቀማ፡ ቅጥል፡ ዕፀ፡ <unclear>ዘዌለጥ፡</unclear> ናጨ፡
                              ቅጥል፡ የሬት፡ ስር፡ የምጽር፡ አባይ፡ ዘርጭ፡ አባይ፡ የጠሌገጅ፡ ስራቸውን፡ የገተም፡ ቅርፊት፡ የብስና፡
                              ቅርፊት፡ የንኩይ፡ ቅርፊት፡ ለወባ፡ መድኃኒት፡ በማር፡ <unclear>ዋጥ፡</unclear></q>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <locus target="#1r #1v"/>
                           <desc>Pen trials.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
